## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible reasons for team failure. The data is limited to the perspectives of the authors and organizations cited, which may introduce bias. Additionally, the rapidly changing dynamics of team environments, especially in technology-driven landscapes, may mean that some insights quickly become outdated.

